Package presenter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LoadXML
    This class is used to load all the objects from an XML file.
    SlideContent
    This class contain all the code for creating new slides in the presentation.
    StartPage
    This class implements the EyeView Start Page.
    StartPage.BannerPictures
    This class sets the ImageView holders for the picture banner images.
    StartPage.PicturesBanner
    This class defines the working of the picture banner.
    Window
    This class is the top-level class that contains the methods for running the MultiMedia Presentation Environment, and run the EyeView software.
    Window.arrowKeyEvent
    This class implements the event handler for switching between XML slides with the left and right arrow keys.
